hm effect and nuclear\nmagnetic resonance studies. In condensed matter physics, we discuss the role of\nthe geometric phase in the theory of the quantum Hall effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Aug 2010 14:46:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2010 13:39:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-09-13"}
